products.title: Leyton Deep Navy Roman Blind

The hue is a classic choice for bringing colour into a space without overwhelming its surroundings, muted and heavy, great for harmonising with deep grey dark, bold and refined, this leyton deep navy roman blind combines a soft, natural feel with stately chic to great effect.
